---
title: Arrabbiata Style Bacon, Spinach and Ricotta Ravioli with Chilli Flakes and Cheese
description: Arrabbiata is a spicy and tart tomato sauce hailing from Italy. Laden with garlic, tomatoes and chilli, it pairs perfectly with the creamy filling of this pasta in our Arrabbiata Style Bacon, Spinach and Ricotta Ravioli.
